{"TopicId":223577,"ForumId":120,"TopicTitle":"Mars Rover is driving like on ice?","CreatedByName":"Ph03nX","CreatedById":218904,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-02-08T20:58:17Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Ph03nX","CreatedById":218904,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-02-08T20:58:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDear KSP comunity,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m not sure if this should be a bug report or just a suggestion.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn any case, please see the videos below - my self-build mars rover is driving like he is on an ice lake. It has a giant turning circle, and is extremely sluggish. Front wheels are set to steer, rear wheels are set to only drive, like on a \u0022normal\u0022 car or rover.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://streamable.com/vz9bap\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://streamable.com/vz9bap\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://streamable.com/dkicqx\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://streamable.com/dkicqx\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kdaviper","CreatedById":229094,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-02-09T16:18:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat is your friction control set to?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ph03nX","CreatedById":218904,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-02-09T18:54:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s set to automatic.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kdaviper","CreatedById":229094,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-02-10T19:56:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224365441\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022223577\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221707504861\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022218904\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Ph03nX\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 2/9/2024 at 1:54 PM, Ph03nX said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s set to automatic.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTurn it off auto and mess with the settings there. Suspension tweaks may help as well.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}